Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.53,0:01:37.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.07,0:01:41.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裏簽名吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.84,0:01:42.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簽名？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.70,0:01:46.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在舊校舍搞什麼活動嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.89,0:01:47.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試膽大會
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.51,0:01:50.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fscx80\fscy92\fnDFPTFLeiSho-W5}屜{\r}田
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.01,0:01:54.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不聚集一定的人數就無法拿到使用許可
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.71,0:01:55.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.81,0:01:58.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺很有趣吧  是{\fe128\fscx80\fscy92\fnDFPTFLeiSho-W5}屜{\r}田的提議
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.55,0:01:59.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.27,0:02:00.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.66,0:02:06.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.24,0:02:07.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.60,0:02:09.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很意外吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.07,0:02:15.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒想到高傲的班長要舉辦鬼怪大會
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.90,0:02:17.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.45,0:02:22.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那確定後跟你聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.30,0:02:24.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.73,0:02:27.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.83,0:02:34.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然看不見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.20,0:02:39.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟…糟了  再見
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.02,0:02:40.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.16,0:02:42.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙怎麼了  突然慌慌張張的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.51,0:02:48.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.18,0:03:00.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不追過來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.45,0:03:03.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.79,0:03:07.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是夏目玲子大人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.65,0:03:11.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  玲子是我祖母  她已經去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.24,0:03:13.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把友人帳交出來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.27,0:03:16.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不交出來就吃了你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.47,0:03:18.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.30,0:03:20.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓咪老師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.88,0:03:22.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別妨礙我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.38,0:03:27.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是你這種低級妖怪能使用的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.88,0:03:28.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.87,0:03:33.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且有他死後友人帳歸我的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.93,0:03:35.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說我已經預約了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.82,0:03:37.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.25,0:03:42.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要消失的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.31,0:03:45.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.85,0:03:48.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾吧  不知天高地厚的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.81,0:03:55.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  解決了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.17,0:03:57.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  老師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.19,0:04:02.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝禮就要七{\fe128\fscx80\fscy92\fnDFPTFLeiSho-W5}辻{\r}屋的包子好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.27,0:04:04.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很喜歡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.56,0:04:10.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為友人帳而找上門的妖怪有兩種
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.17,0:04:18.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一種是像剛才一樣想統治被寫了名字的妖怪而來搶友人帳的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.10,0:04:21.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一種則是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.39,0:04:24.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.10,0:04:28.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來討回寫在友人帳上的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.65,0:04:37.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個包子多少都吃得下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.50,0:04:41.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  又歸還名字了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.99,0:04:42.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.97,0:04:44.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是多此一舉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.33,0:04:47.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友人帳越來越薄了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.39,0:04:51.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歸還名字後非常疲憊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.22,0:05:00.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我拿到時還能剩幾隻呢  乾脆吃了這小鬼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.52,0:05:03.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽到了哦  你這只冒牌招財貓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.59,0:05:08.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.24,0:05:10.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多吃點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.15,0:05:14.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔子阿姨開朗而溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.30,0:05:17.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滋叔叔話比較少  但一直很溫和
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.82,0:05:21.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不想給他們添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.88,0:05:26.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不吃呢  貓咪它
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.02,0:05:33.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這可添了個大麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.37,0:05:36.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它不吃剩飯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.52,0:05:37.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.76,0:05:42.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.45,0:05:44.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢  看來是個美食家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.57,0:05:45.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.23,0:05:50.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？這是牙痕？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.79,0:05:54.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲  真是美味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.03,0:05:58.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  貴志
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.46,0:06:00.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不小心嗆到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.74,0:06:05.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好塔子阿姨他們看不見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.47,0:06:09.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目大人  請把名字還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.28,0:06:11.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.48,0:06:15.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細一看你不是露神老頭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.99,0:06:18.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認識他嗎  老師
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.90,0:06:22.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  因為變小了我沒認出來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.02,0:06:23.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這個聲音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.21,0:06:26.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊  你是斑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.11,0:06:31.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼變成這副可笑的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.08,0:06:32.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵囉嗦  我吃了你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.02,0:06:35.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.32,0:06:40.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾之守護喲  昭顯其名
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.14,0:06:49.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.64,0:06:53.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  跟後面一張粘在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.44,0:06:56.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢  完全粘在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.19,0:06:58.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是米粒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.02,0:06:59.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米粒？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.31,0:07:04.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲子總是馬馬虎虎的  一邊吃飯一邊玩友人帳了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.79,0:07:05.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.74,0:07:12.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…別硬拉開  皮膚像針刺一樣痛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.49,0:07:15.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告訴過你吧  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.50,0:07:17.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字被破壞身體就會裂開
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.96,0:07:19.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燒掉的話身體也會變成灰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.83,0:07:22.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對哦  抱歉了  露神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.33,0:07:25.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.28,0:07:30.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這種情況  請你放棄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.23,0:07:31.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.56,0:07:35.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴志  可以來洗澡了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.53,0:07:36.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.11,0:07:39.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎能如此無情…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.62,0:07:43.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為揭不下來啊  我想還也還不了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.79,0:07:45.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想想辦法吧  夏目大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.73,0:07:48.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把名字還給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.04,0:07:50.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法就是沒辦法嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.00,0:07:53.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.49,0:08:05.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露神就住在前面的七森
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.65,0:08:09.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我拿來我就帶了  但這東西用來幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.48,0:08:12.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以防萬一  反正先收起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.26,0:08:22.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.54,0:08:25.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼  給
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.54,0:08:30.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你的好心  沒摔壞的話就拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.54,0:08:33.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一個人也吃不了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.43,0:08:36.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  那我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.70,0:08:42.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天氣真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.90,0:08:46.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.92,0:08:47.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.57,0:08:58.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候如果能作出更好的回應
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.33,0:09:00.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真討厭自己的不善言辭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.58,0:09:03.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個老太太活不長了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.86,0:09:07.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氣息不太美味
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.19,0:09:10.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說失禮的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.39,0:09:17.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是露神的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.73,0:09:19.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  露出這種表情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.54,0:09:22.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露神不只是名字  而是真正的神明啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.82,0:09:27.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來了啊  夏目大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.67,0:09:32.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  昨天做了那麼多失禮的事  會遭報應的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.59,0:09:34.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲子啊  你怎麼做這種遭天譴的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.33,0:09:36.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.76,0:09:40.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙知道你是真正的神明驚慌失措了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.70,0:09:42.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  露神…大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.81,0:09:45.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.43,0:09:51.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然被稱為神明  其實以前我是住在這祠堂的無家可歸的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.82,0:09:56.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前這裏遭過嚴重的乾旱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.88,0:10:01.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村裏的年輕人擔憂慘狀  向這個祠堂祈願
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.50,0:10:04.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰巧第二天下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.48,0:10:08.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後村人就把這個祠堂拜為露神
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.54,0:10:11.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還放上很多供品
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.29,0:10:18.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我察覺到時已經充滿了力量  身體也變得像樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.87,0:10:19.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像樣了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.35,0:10:22.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前看到他時身體還跟人類一樣大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.21,0:10:25.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在人跡罕至了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.62,0:10:31.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以憑借信仰成長的身體也縮小成這般模樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.03,0:10:32.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.77,0:10:36.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你桃子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.88,0:10:40.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃子我也有哦  你看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.90,0:10:42.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.23,0:10:46.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你見到小花了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.86,0:10:49.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  她叫小花啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.90,0:10:53.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是現在唯一會來這裏叩拜的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.79,0:10:58.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.61,0:11:04.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  只要把粘在一起的名字也歸還掉就不用強行揭開了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.39,0:11:08.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有一個大問題
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.39,0:11:11.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不認識另一個妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.80,0:11:14.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認識他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.36,0:11:16.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.91,0:11:19.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敗給玲子後我很不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.15,0:11:27.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說下一個被奪走名字的妖怪後我為了痛快去看過他的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.05,0:11:29.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  畫完了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.84,0:11:31.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字雖然不記得了  他是長這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.85,0:11:35.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.52,0:11:37.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我畫得真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.18,0:11:40.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有…毛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.17,0:11:43.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有毛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.36,0:11:43.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一根也沒有？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.58,0:11:45.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一根也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.57,0:11:50.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時他住在參之塚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.70,0:11:53.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是陰影之主  利用陰影移動
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.40,0:11:55.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.77,0:12:05.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑什麼  嘲笑我的畫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.29,0:12:12.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們會遭報應的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.70,0:12:23.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們開始在參之塚尋找這只妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.79,0:12:31.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但花了好幾天也沒能找到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.97,0:12:37.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  好像很困
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.66,0:12:38.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搜索太累了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.23,0:12:40.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.81,0:12:49.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊  小花她看不見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.30,0:12:52.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明就在能感覺到呼吸的咫尺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.44,0:12:57.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.02,0:13:00.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也來參拜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.24,0:13:01.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.58,0:13:07.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  最近好像只有我來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.90,0:13:11.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還怕露神大人寂寞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.96,0:13:14.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您從什麼時候開始來參拜的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.71,0:13:15.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從小時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.22,0:13:21.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請別見笑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.46,0:13:27.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感覺自己見過一次露神大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.65,0:13:33.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女子學校放學回家路上  也是像今天一樣的好天氣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.06,0:13:38.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像平時一樣參拜完抬起頭時
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.24,0:13:41.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到祠堂後面有一隻腳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.98,0:13:44.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然嚇了一跳  但我裝作沒看見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.12,0:13:51.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後看到戴著老翁面具的人很舒服的坐著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.18,0:13:55.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說了句今天真是好天氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.39,0:14:00.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我差點就要回答說是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.27,0:14:06.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但感覺到被人類看見露神大人就會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.25,0:14:12.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可現在還在想  如果當時大膽地回答了他就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.63,0:14:16.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為露神大人總是一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.28,0:14:19.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我一定會寂寞難耐了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.59,0:14:22.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以至少應該用聲音回應
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.77,0:14:30.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.23,0:14:33.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.39,0:14:35.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人很寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.58,0:14:37.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.33,0:14:42.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人…很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.68,0:14:49.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛苦…好重
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.30,0:14:56.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別睡傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.56,0:15:04.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚做惡夢了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.84,0:15:06.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是老師太重了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.40,0:15:09.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你的內心有破綻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.40,0:15:11.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軟弱的心會呼喚魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.61,0:15:16.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想丟掉性命就時刻不能放鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.12,0:15:24.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過對我來說還是你早點丟掉性命  讓我早點拿到友人帳比較開心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.97,0:15:28.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再睡傻就拔掉你尾巴上的毛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.16,0:15:29.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這惡魔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.75,0:15:32.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想被妖怪說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.26,0:15:36.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了  夏目大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.07,0:15:39.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.86,0:15:42.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那傢伙果然在這山裏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.72,0:15:46.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出聲叫他就跑了  但應該還沒走遠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.98,0:15:48.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  兵分兩路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.30,0:15:49.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.37,0:15:50.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.28,0:15:52.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼麻煩的東西來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.14,0:15:53.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.91,0:15:58.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.24,0:16:14.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.07,0:16:17.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這傢伙  他主動出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.49,0:16:18.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟畫完全不一樣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.38,0:16:21.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼蠢話  分明一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.59,0:16:23.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有那個字是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.82,0:16:24.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  用鏡子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.42,0:16:27.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用陽光反射  弄暈他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.03,0:16:28.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.28,0:16:29.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.58,0:16:32.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.41,0:16:39.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.50,0:16:43.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.45,0:16:46.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.24,0:16:53.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參上前來取食物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.24,0:16:55.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.20,0:16:58.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.20,0:17:02.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我決勝負吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.59,0:17:07.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏過我就給你食物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.81,0:17:10.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者把我吃掉也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.74,0:17:15.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是玲子  你的名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.45,0:17:20.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  他的名字是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.53,0:17:22.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.58,0:17:24.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.14,0:17:38.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濯  露神  把名字還給你們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.06,0:17:55.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽見了嗎  露神
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.76,0:17:58.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽見了  玲子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.81,0:18:01.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,供品不會一直持續的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.73,0:18:04.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上今天就連一個桃子都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.07,0:18:06.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.29,0:18:09.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類就是嚴厲和無情的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.59,0:18:13.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁著力量還在找個更好的住處比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.63,0:18:16.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  玲子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.52,0:18:22.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但一旦被愛過  去愛過
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.38,0:18:26.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就無法忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.52,0:18:33.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.24,0:18:40.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經能走路了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.91,0:18:45.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個叫濯的妖怪  利用陰影來到村裏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.12,0:18:50.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為拿走剩飯的回報會幫那家人洗完盤子才離開
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.54,0:18:52.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？你調查過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.09,0:18:55.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在街上連晚上也很明亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.83,0:18:57.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會再見到他了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.55,0:19:02.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山裏也有同伴  跟人類斷絕來往  那傢伙也輕鬆了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.18,0:19:05.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  真是那樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.83,0:19:12.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露神  我帶桃子來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.88,0:19:15.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露神？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.12,0:19:17.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裏  夏目大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.07,0:19:22.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又變小了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.03,0:19:23.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.42,0:19:30.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你發光了  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.27,0:19:34.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小花走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.94,0:19:38.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小花長年患病
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.82,0:19:41.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近來一次也不容易了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.53,0:19:49.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小花是最後一個信奉我的人類  她走了的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.46,0:19:50.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.04,0:19:53.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來信奉你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.78,0:19:55.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天來雖然很難  但我也會來叩拜的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.34,0:20:01.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  夏目大人  你是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.26,0:20:03.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.03,0:20:06.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能跟小花一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.30,0:20:18.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直  一直僅僅是看著她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.22,0:20:26.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣終於…終於感覺能夠觸及她了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.36,0:20:34.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小花她聽見了…你的聲音  露神
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.11,0:20:38.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  夏目大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.54,0:20:46.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論以前還是現在  都覺得人類真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.92,0:21:01.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天天氣真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.72,0:21:02.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.44,0:21:07.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.57,0:21:20.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.38,0:21:23.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你幹什麼啊  好浪費
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.79,0:21:26.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說這種會遭天譴的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.36,0:21:29.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏什麼都沒有！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.83,0:21:32.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算今天沒有  也許明天就有了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.16,0:21:34.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思念的心最重要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.34,0:21:43.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼  這只蠢貓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.78,0:21:45.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是招財貓啊  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.48,0:21:49.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.99,0:21:52.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵什麼喵  把包子還我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.12,0:21:56.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  慢著  包子小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.38,0:21:57.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的包子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.76,0:22:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我買的吧  等等  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.91,0:22:02.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.39,0:22:04.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵～喵～
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.99,0:23:41.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  夏目  八原的妖怪們哭著說被人類欺負了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.00,0:23:44.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是能看見妖怪的人幹的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.47,0:23:46.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙很可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.00,0:23:47.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.30,0:23:50.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是田沼要
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.18,0:23:51.19,biaoti1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(140,550)}八原的怪人
